data.description: Beautifully remodeled Twinhome with no restrictions, no HOA. Brand new custom kitchen cabinets with soft close drawers, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, undermounted sink, lighting, faucet, hardware backsplash and floors! All new lighting, luxury vinyl plank flooring and fresh paint throughout. Tastefully updated bath with gorgeous vanity, sink, mirror and lighting. Fully fenced yard with firepit and large storage shed. Front patio area. Very convenient location. All living on one level with a bright, homey feel. Affordable and Adorable!
